<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/OKJI> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "This is a normalised version of the dependence count non-uniformity feature" .
# 
# http://www.radiomics.org/RO/OKUW
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/OKUW> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
