<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/RNU0> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The volume V is calculated from the ROI mesh as indicated in https://doi.org/10.1109/ICIP.2001.958278" .
# 
# http://www.radiomics.org/RO/S5ZE
