<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/SALO> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The interquartile range (IQR) is defined as P75 - P25, where P75 is the 75th percentile of the image matrix, and P25 is the 25th" .
# 
# http://www.radiomics.org/RO/SKGS
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/SKGS> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/SKGS> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.radiomics.org/RO/HCUG> .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/SKGS> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> "IBSI" .
