<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/SKGS> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The Compactness defines the deviation of the ROI volume from a perfect sphere. Compactness 1 is a measure of how compact, or sphere-like or sphere like the volume is" .
# 
