<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/SWZ1> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The volume density minimum volume enclosing ellipsoid is the ratio between the volume and the minimum volume enclosing ellipsoid, calculated as in https://doi.org/10.1016/j.dam.2007.02.013" .
# 
