<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/SXLW> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> "IBSI" .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/SXLW> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "GLRLM_RunLengthVariance" .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/SXLW> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "This feature estimates the variance in runs for run lengths" .
# 
# http://www.radiomics.org/RO/TDIC
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/TDIC> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/TDIC> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.radiomics.org/RO/HCUG> .
