# 
# http://www.radiomics.org/RO/TP0I
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/TP0I> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/TP0I> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.radiomics.org/RO/ZOEY> .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/TP0I> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Grey Level Run Length Matrix (GLRLM)" .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/TP0I> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The Grey level run length matrix (GLRLM) like the grey level co-occurrence matrix, GLRLM also assesses the distribution of discretised grey levels in an image or in a stack of images. However, instead of assessing the combination of levels between neighbouring pixels or voxels, GLRLM assesses grey level run lengths. Run length counts the frequency of consecutive voxels with discretised grey level i along direction delta" .
# 
