<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/3NSA> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "GLSZM_ZoneSizeVariance" .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/3NSA> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "This feature estimates the variance in zone counts for the different zone sizes" .
# 
# http://www.radiomics.org/RO/3S2S
