<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/3YWD> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.radiomics.org/RO/JCNR> .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/3YWD> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "RietsFilter" .
# 
# http://www.radiomics.org/RO/4BEG
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/4BEG> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/4BEG> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.radiomics.org/RO/JCNR> .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/4BEG> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "WaveletFilter" .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/4BEG> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "This filter decomposes an image in wavelets. A wavelet series is a representation of a square-integrable (real- or complex-valued) function by a certain orthonormal series generated by a wavelet" .
# 
# http://www.radiomics.org/RO/4FUA
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/4FUA> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/4FUA> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.radiomics.org/RO/UHIW> .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/4FUA> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> "IBSI" .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/4FUA> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "MeanAbsoluteDeviation" .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/4FUA> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The mean of the absolute deviations of all voxel intensities around the mean intensitity value" .
# 
# http://www.radiomics.org/RO/4JP3
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/4JP3> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/4JP3> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.radiomics.org/RO/9SAK> .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/4JP3> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> "IBSI" .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/4JP3> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "GLSZM_ZoneSizeNonUniformity" .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/4JP3> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "This features assesses the distribution of zone counts over the different zone sizes. The feature value is low when zone counts are equally distributed along zone sizes" .
# 
# http://www.radiomics.org/RO/4S59
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/4S59> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/4S59> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.radiomics.org/RO/HCUG> .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/4S59> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> "Pyradiomics" .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/4S59> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Maximum2DDiameterSlice" .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/4S59> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Maximum 2D diameter (Slice) is defined as the largest pairwise Euclidean distance between tumor surface voxels in the row-column (generally the axial) plane." .
# 
# http://www.radiomics.org/RO/4S5Z
