<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/4YPT> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.radiomics.org/RO/V7MM> .
# 
# http://www.radiomics.org/RO/48P8
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/48P8> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/48P8> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.radiomics.org/RO/9SAK> .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/48P8> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> "IBSI" .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/48P8> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "GLSZM_LargeZoneEmphasis" .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/48P8> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "This feature emphasises large zones" .
# 
# http://www.radiomics.org/RO/5ABU
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/5ABU> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/5ABU> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.radiomics.org/RO/HCUG> .
