<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/5ABU> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Maximum2DDiameterColumn" .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/5ABU> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Maximum 2D diameter (Column) is defined as the largest pairwise Euclidean distance between tumor surface voxels in the row-slice (usually the coronal) plane." .
# 
# http://www.radiomics.org/RO/5GN9
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/5GN9> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/5GN9> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.radiomics.org/RO/9SAK> .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/5GN9> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> "IBSI" .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/5GN9> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "GLSZM_HighGreyLevelZoneEmphasis" .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/5GN9> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Measures the distribution of the higher gray-level values, with a higher value indicating a greater proportion of higher gray-level values and size zones in the image" .
# 
# http://www.radiomics.org/RO/5QRC
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/5QRC> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/5QRC> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.radiomics.org/RO/9SAK> .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/5QRC> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> "IBSI" .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/5QRC> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "GLSZM_SmallZoneEmphasis" .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/5QRC> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "This feature emphasises small zones" .
# 
# http://www.radiomics.org/RO/5RAI
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/5RAI> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/5RAI> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.radiomics.org/RO/9SAK> .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/5RAI> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> "IBSI" .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/5RAI> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "GLSZM_SmallZoneLowGreyLevelEmphasis" .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/5RAI> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "This feature emphasises runs in the upper left quadrant of the GLSZM, where small zone sizes and low grey levels are located" .
# 
# http://www.radiomics.org/RO/5SPA
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/5SPA> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
