<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/60VM> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.radiomics.org/RO/LFYI> .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/60VM> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> "IBSI" .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/60VM> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "GLCM_JointAverage" .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/60VM> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The grey level weigthed sum of joint probabilities" .
# 
# http://www.radiomics.org/RO/62GR
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/62GR> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/62GR> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.radiomics.org/RO/1XL1> .
# 
# http://www.radiomics.org/RO/65HE
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/65HE> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/65HE> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.radiomics.org/RO/IPET> .
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/65HE> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> "IBSI" .
