<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/mCODERadiomics#DosiomicsFeatures> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Advanced field of study in radiation therapy. Instead of looking at a medical image like an X-ray or MRI, dosiomics extracts high-dimensional, minable mathematical data directly from a patient's 3D radiation dose distributions." .
