<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/mCODERadiomics#mCR_0000261> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Data structure used to transmit measurements, test results, and clinical assessments made about a patient" .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/mCODERadiomics#mCR_0000261> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Observation"@en .
