<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/mCODERadiomics#mCR_0000265> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Lansky Play Performance Status"@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/mCODERadiomics#mCR_0000265> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The Lansky Play-Performance Status for children is a parent-rated instrument which records usual play activity as the index of performance. It is similar to the Karnofsky Performance Scale for adults" .
